From `docs/plugins/sdk-channel-plugins.md`:

### Step 1: Package & Manifest
```json
{
  "name": "@myorg/openclaw-pulseboard",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "type": "module",
  "openclaw": {
    "extensions": ["./index.ts"],
    "setupEntry": "./setup-entry.ts",
