## 3. Plugin Manifest Format (`openclaw.plugin.json`)

### Minimal Example:
```json
{
  "id": "pulseboard",
  "configSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "properties": {
      "pulseboard": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "token": { "type": "string" },
          "allowFrom": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Rich Example (Channel Plugin):
```json
{
  "id": "pulseboard",
  "kind": "channel",
  "channels": ["pulseboard"],
  "name": "PulseBoard",
  "description": "PulseBoard channel plugin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "configSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "properties": {
      "pulseboard": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "token": { "type": "string" },
          "allowFrom": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
          "dmSecurity": { "type": "string" }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "uiHints": {
    "token": {
      "label": "API Token",
      "sensitive": true,
      "placeholder": "pb_..."
    }
  }
}
```

### Top-Level Fields:
| Field | Required | Type | Purpose |
|-------|----------|------|---------|
| `id` | Yes | string | Plugin identifier |
| `configSchema` | Yes | object | JSON Schema for config validation |
| `channels` | No | string[] | Channel ids this plugin owns |
| `providers` | No | string[] | Provider ids this plugin owns |
| `kind` | No | string | Plugin kind ("memory", "context-engine") |
| `name` | No | string | Human-readable name |
| `description` | No | string | Short description |
| `version` | No | string | Plugin version |
| `uiHints` | No | object | UI labels & hints for config fields |
| `contracts` | No | object | Static capability ownership |
| `enabledByDefault` | No | boolean | Bundled plugin enabled by default |

