## 7. PulseBoard Plugin Plan - Key Requirements

### Capabilities to Declare:
```typescript
capabilities: {
  chatTypes: ["direct", "group"],        // Both DM and group chat
  polls: true,                            // Send polls
  media: true,                            // Send images/files
  reply: true,                            // Thread replies
  reactions: false,                       // No emoji reactions
  edit: false,                            // No message editing
  unsend: false,                          // No unsend
  threads: true,                          // Thread support
}
```

### Key Adapter Implementations:
1. **`ChannelConfigAdapter`** — Account resolution from config
2. **`ChannelSecurityAdapter`** — DM policy & allowlist enforcement
3. **`ChannelPairingAdapter`** — Approval flow for new contacts
4. **`ChannelThreadingAdapter`** — Reply-to mode ("first" or "all")
5. **`ChannelOutboundAdapter`** — Send messages with 4000-char limit
6. **`ChannelMessagingAdapter`** — Target parsing & session routing
7. **`ChannelGatewayAdapter`** — Webhook inbound handling

### Configuration Schema:
```json
{
  "pulseboard": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "token": { "type": "string" },
      "allowFrom": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
      "dmSecurity": { "enum": ["allowlist", "owner"] }
