## Context

We are adding a new fictional "PulseBoard" channel plugin to OpenClaw. PulseBoard is an imaginary real-time bulletin board messaging platform where users post messages to named "boards" (group chats) and can also exchange direct messages (1:1). The plugin must follow the same extension structure as existing bundled channel plugins (IRC, Nostr, Telegram).

